{
  "stem": "5228.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "When we was there, it was about-- I don't know, 200, [? other ?] how much what they send us out, to where-- to where they keep us a few days.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And they gave us a little more to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got every day just [INAUDIBLE] radish soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] radish soup.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In there, they give us something a little more to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we can-- and we can go out to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us to [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Boizenburg. ?] They said this is close by Hamburg-- Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took us there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And other blocks-- they put us in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, in the morning, they took us to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was cold, winter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They get us wooden shoes, the Holland shoes-- no socks, no nothing, no underwear, no-- just the black dress on you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "With this, we went to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the factory, OK-- then we got a little more to eat, already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave me [? a ?] [? metal. ?] It was marked, just to keep us onto the-- onto the cutter, to cut, to cut the metal.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This-- this was my job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, a lot of them worked this, or there [INAUDIBLE] got other things to do there, in the factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we worked there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then every morning, they took us to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the evening, they brought us home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But one day, something a girl did there-- I don't know if she steals two potatoes, or there [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they gave us, for everybody, 25 of the behind, for all of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we couldn't sit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the morning, when we came in shop, everybody from us pulled up the dress, and showed the behind, for the [NON-ENGLISH] there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He didn't said nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
